                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7712" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR-0206</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1122 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">跑道中的孤勇者：道一公司履行企业社会责任之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Health is more important than everything: The way that Daoyi chose fulfills their social responsibility</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">邵霞琳，蔡鲁祥，朱世峰，陈雨竹，张友军，王瑛之</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">宁波财经学院*</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">道一高分子聚合物（宁波）有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">化学工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">17 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业社会责任；金字塔模型；困境；对策</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Enterprise Social Responsibility; Pyramid of Corporate Social Responsibility；dilemma;Countermeasures</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">积极履行企业社会责任是当前企业发展的重要趋势，企业社会责任不仅仅是在经济、法律、伦理方面，还体现在慈善上。本案例描述了安全跑道生产中的“孤勇者”——道一公司总经理岑建达一直坚守创业时承担社会责任的初心，创业过程中先后遇到技术难题、招投标困境、市场等问题。在社会责任的驱使下，他坚守初心，追逐利润的同时承担起经济、法律、伦理和慈善等企业社会责任，帮助企业走出困境的故事。通过对案例企业社会责任履行过程的回顾和现状的描述，以此解读企业社会责任金字塔模型理论，引导学生理解企业社会责任理论、卡罗尔四层金字塔模型的概念，掌握金字塔模型的应用、如何在履行企业社会责任的同时突破难关、发展创新。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">To actively fulfill corporate social responsibility is a great trend.As an important trend in the development of enterprises, corporate social responsibility is not only reflected in economy, law and ethics, but also in charity. This case describes the &quot;lonly braver&quot; in the production of safe runways - Cen Jianda, the general manager of Daoyi Company, has always adhered to the original intention of assuming social responsibility when starting a business, who encountered technical difficulties, bidding difficulties,market and other issues, driven by social responsibility.He adheres to the original aspiration, in the pursuit of profits at the same time to assume the “Pyramid of Corporate Social Responsibility”.The “Pyramid of Corporate Social Responsibility” theory of economic, legal, ethical and philanthropic corporate social responsibility helps the enterprises out of trouble. Through the case of corporate social responsibility implementation process review and the description of the current situation helps to interpret corporate social responsibility Pyramid model theory, guide students to understand the theory of corporate social responsibility, company Grasp the application of pyramid model, how to break through difficulties by fulfilling corporate social responsibility, develop and innovate.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业社会责任》、《管理学》、《商业伦理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例主要围绕企业社会责任，在具体的理论知识方面，包含：企业社会责任企业社会责任金字塔模型及企业履行社会责任的驱动力、利益相关者理论、企业社会责任履行、不同阶段企业社会责任管理发展理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-10</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
